{"tid":921182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打麻將摸到槓上開花　支那女子太興奮致高血壓病發猝死","createTime":"2018-11-29T10:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T12:37:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6880cf6bb69e250fe74143cf9a7169dc8cca9e","tid":921182,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"俗話說樂極生悲，最近中國大陸重慶有名女子，疑似因為打麻將自摸太興奮，以至於高血壓病發猝死。<br />\n <br />\n大陸媒體報導，47歲文姓女子本月19日中午到住家附近麻將館打牌時，突然自摸槓上花，讓她興奮得不得了，沒想到下一刻她就忽然倒下。<br />\n <br />\n牌友立刻跑到對面診所找醫生救命，但醫師到現場後發現文女已經瞳孔放大，沒了生命跡象。<br />\n <br />\n死者丈夫表示，妻子兩年前被診斷罹患高血壓，以前也吃過藥，但自己對病情並不在意。親戚先前也曾多次勸告愛打麻將的妻子，以後不要再去打牌以免情緒激動，但她仍是一有時間就往麻將館跑。<br />\n <br />\n當地媒體在報導最後還呼籲有心血管疾病的民眾，參加娛樂體育活動要量力而行，切忌大悲大喜，以免遭遇意外。"},{"pid":"4207ba3dc5ef509dd0ce2043820721c85fc5b881","tid":921182,"uid":203417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"咁咲要死幾多次？"},{"pid":"dd091a6e88e2e15be0d679880b9f71c0f2ff59a7","tid":921182,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4207ba3dc5ef509dd0ce2043820721c85fc5b881","tid":921182,"uid":203417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"咁咲要死幾多次？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"[img<a href=\"https://blogimg.goo.ne.jp/user_image/65/87/4ed152e90bf2b01fc7cef3899ac6f89c.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogimg.goo.ne.jp%2Fuser_image%2F65%2F87%2F4ed152e90bf2b01fc7cef3899ac6f89c.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=614118de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogimg.goo.ne.jp/user_image/65/87/4ed152e90bf2b01fc7cef3899ac6f89c.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://blogimg.goo.ne.jp/user_image/7b/3a/9d4070d1bc65a5b83c2a72684148cf04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogimg.goo.ne.jp%2Fuser_image%2F7b%2F3a%2F9d4070d1bc65a5b83c2a72684148cf04.jpg&h=6e67d7f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n示意圖"},{"pid":"54ba90d48